metadata.name: The Last Nakasupper
metadata.description: The Last Nakasupper happened on the 23rd of March before the official launch of Nakamigos. SUSEJ gathered the diverse representatives of each Migo town to give them his blessing. From ninjas to snowmen to knight to invisibles to bots to caped men and many more, SUSEJ and his twelve Migosciples commit to a mission to push the Nakamigos forward and together to fulfill the prophecy of the collection mooning.  "Come, follow me, Migo."
